-random zone loot from ODS to gems very nice if ya get lucky<br>
<br>
Upper ring of seru is also challenging solo.  Chance of adds if you are not careful and they hit hard enough to keep things interesting.<br>
-15 to 20pp average on these guys<br>
-lucid shard for VT key later in your career<br>
<br>
Breaking the zone in of HS I hear is quite challenging.  I've done it duo and it can be interesting.<br>
<br>
Check out the zone in of Acryilya caverns.  Very challenging managing the HT's and adds should you mis-time the wanderer.  Fast respawn time.<br>
-Ore's used in trades<br>
<br>
Thats all I have for now.  All in all if you want a challenge I find there is much more for the person who duo's.<br>
